{"tid":2439482,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黨政府回應日本券商撤走：仍有1450家券商 歡迎繼續借香港為跳板投資中國","createTime":"2021-03-09T09:39:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T10:21:42.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fe8c80b2442081105a7860e9962ff682934a170a","tid":2439482,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T09:39:08.000Z","msg":"財庫局：維護國家安全與香港發展利益相輔相成<br />\n<br />\n財經事務及庫務局回應指，維護國家安全與香港發展利益相輔相成，當局會繼續致力提高香港作為國際金融中心的地位，善用香港與內地及國際的連通優勢，抓緊粵港澳大灣區及國家內外雙循環策略的發展機遇，匯聚國際投資者自由參與香港市場。<br />\n<br />\n當局又指，香港的資本市場一直運作暢順，並保持活躍，在2019年底至2020年底期間，在香港從事證券交易的持牌法團數目有所增加，達約1450家，去年香港股市集資3975億港元，按年上升26.5%，全球位居第二。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2382148\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2382148&d=eGp%2FCvHI00KNC8mlo1MhyytC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=98731098\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2382148</a>"},{"pid":"131fbd0dd1b5c790678dcc20937a62e4f9e63286","tid":2439482,"uid":11291,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T09:43:44.000Z","msg":"開口埋口都係大灣區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94a9681c9897e5b21b3b12886ccf12ea43c646ac","tid":2439482,"uid":33868,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T09:44:37.000Z","msg":"借香港做跳板<br />\n有咩跳板個原地同目的地係一樣？"},{"pid":"b3d8dd4b116ac1ceac2c96d8363e2a245c9e6c1c","tid":2439482,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T09:45:44.000Z","msg":"有耀才就得啦<br />\nD廣告咁'高質'<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8beeece878acfaecd47a843dca905ea7f8d4778f","tid":2439482,"uid":320902,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T09:46:17.000Z","msg":"點解唔借上海做跳板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8a90facfe0d5bbbdf98c6ce3c1233a5942cfc14","tid":2439482,"uid":241399,"like":0,"dislike":0